OL,3,CWoman donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FA woman from Guernsey has donated 10
OL,7,Fnew treatment chairs to the cancer
OL,8,Funit at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FAnne Hutchings lost her husband,
OL,12,FMichael, to cancer and donated the
OL,13,Fchairs along with new furniture in
OL,14,Frecognition of the care her husband
OL,15,Freceived whilst undergoing treatment.
OL,17,FThe new chairs are remote control
OL,18,Foperated, which can assist people
OL,19,Fgetting up and have ports so patients
OL,20,Fcan charge their phones or laptops.
