OL,3,CWoman donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FAnne says: "It was because my husband
OL,7,Fsat in a small chair, always in one
OL,8,Fplace, he was quite comfortable but
OL,9,Fsome people came and they had to stay
OL,10,Ffor a whole morning or an afternoon or
OL,11,Feven the whole day.
OL,13,F"It was just the case of can we get
OL,14,Fsomething more comfortable, something
OL,15,Fbetter that people can nestle into,
OL,16,Flike an armchair where you can
OL,17,Fcompletely relax."
OL,19,FShe adds: "I think it will make a
OL,20,Fgreat difference, I am thrilled, I am
OL,21,Fover the moon.
