OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,F"Some people might think well a chair
OL,7,Fis a chair but these chairs are rather
OL,8,Fspecial."
OL,10,F"Like an armchair where you can
OL,11,Fcompletely relax"- Anne explains what
OL,12,Finspired her to give back to the
OL,13,Fhospital
OL,15,FLead cancer nurse, Lucy Coggon says:
OL,16,F"The sessions for treatment can be
OL,17,Fanywhere from an hour up to eight
OL,18,Fhours so it can be a really long day
OL,19,Ffor people, so it is really important
OL,20,Fthat people feel comfortable whilst
OL,21,Fthey are here.
