OL,3,CWoman donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,F"The chairs also have a USB port so
OL,7,Fpeople can send messages to friends
OL,8,Fand family whilst undergoing
OL,9,Ftreatment, so it is important that
OL,10,Fpeople have their gadgets fully
OL,11,Fcharged up whilst they are here, so
OL,12,Fthat is lovely."
OL,14,FAnne explains how her childhood played
OL,15,Fa role in her donation: "I grew up
OL,16,Fwith generous parents, parents who
OL,17,Fgave, parents who did not expect to be
OL,18,Fgiven things all the time so I just
OL,19,Ffeel it is part of me to give and my
OL,20,Fhusband was like that too.
