OL,3,CWoman donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,F"Caring to me is giving love and
OL,7,Fappreciation and care for other
OL,8,Fpeople, I had that from my husband and
OL,9,Fmy husband had that from the nurses
OL,10,Fhere, they were warm, welcoming and
OL,11,Fthat is one of the many, many reasons."
OL,13,FA statement from Health and Social
OL,14,FCare says: "The staff and patients in
OL,15,FBulstrode Oncology Unit are grateful
OL,16,Fto Anne for her generosity in funding
OL,17,Fnew furniture for the department.
