OL,3,CWoman donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,F"The day unit provides outpatient
OL,7,Fservices to adults with a cancer
OL,8,Fdiagnosis and treatment sessions can
OL,9,Flast up to 8 hours, so it is important
OL,10,Fthat the chairs are comfortable for
OL,11,Fpeople to sit in for long periods.
OL,13,F"All the new treatment chairs are
OL,14,Fremote control operated and rise and
OL,15,Frecline which can assist people to get
OL,16,Fup when they are attached to a drip.
OL,17,FThey also have a footrest for comfort."
